summary: WWE Backlash 2024, to be held in France, has an anticipated match card and start time. Predictions and rumors suggest that Cody Rhodes may emerge victorious. The event will feature intriguing heel and face turns, and fans can anticipate a thrilling showdown between Rhodes and AJ Styles. Live updates, results, and analysis will be available through various outlets including Yahoo Sports and Last Word On Sports. Streaming options are detailed in articles by Variety, Billboard, and Sports Illustrated, ensuring convenient access for viewers. Digital Trends provides instructions on how to watch the live stream. Forbes highlights potential smart booking decisions, while Bleacher Report analyzes likely character transformations. Sporting News covers the event's date, start time, and other details.
